The following components are derived from cmux:
- Terminal rendering engine (Ghostty-based)
- Workspace and surface management
- Socket control API (v1 and v2 protocols)
- Browser panel integration
- Claude Code hook system
- CLI tool

The following components are original to execuTerm:
- daemon/ — ExecuFunction orchestration daemon (TypeScript)
- ExecuFunction API integration and authentication
- Task dispatch and agent lifecycle management
- Dashboard server

